  "detailed_description": "<h1>Reviews</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Overall the game is pretty fun as survivor-type gameplay goes.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - ~Casual Lovers~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Darkchaser: Battletide got a pretty decent gameplay loop.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Retro Addict</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"чтобы противостоять бесчисленным ордам врагов в ожесточённых сражениях.\" </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Gaming Grandma</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/8b14f29a552aa43ac71743f08ebc3514.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/1eff50f4913f5b80a3f3c8b485cdce52.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/1eff50f4913f5b80a3f3c8b485cdce52.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/1eff50f4913f5b80a3f3c8b485cdce52.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In multiplayer mode, you will compete against another player. Use new relics and skills to see who can fight to the end under dual pressure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/0aa402b6dba2dcbfc3f237ea60b19646.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/8b70e069a268097d109303a44f1f0f33.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/8b70e069a268097d109303a44f1f0f33.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/8b70e069a268097d109303a44f1f0f33.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Bears, bees, cacti... Various summons will serve as loyal assistants on the field. Eliminate enemies more efficiently!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/79aff1caa8ec3f7818e32d619f8eab57.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/3192459048d6e5967681f62bd225ea41.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/3192459048d6e5967681f62bd225ea41.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/3192459048d6e5967681f62bd225ea41.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>During the battle, you can freely choose your builds with various skills, whether it's fire, ice, traps, or poison, all can be the means to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/2dd7a5c30a338a4b766b43b6250df415.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/91ab5cc2b6374e30837b5bb55047d702.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/91ab5cc2b6374e30837b5bb55047d702.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/91ab5cc2b6374e30837b5bb55047d702.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Multiple choices of characters, smash your enemies with different tactics! Unconventional approach or  overwhelming firepower? Melee lover or ranged mastery? Only the most suitable choices ensure survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/419ecb4ef85d065727657ce33717606d.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/89f3756a5f3d5b7591d4bdb660b12da8.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/89f3756a5f3d5b7591d4bdb660b12da8.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/89f3756a5f3d5b7591d4bdb660b12da8.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>After each combat, unexpected relics will enrich your journey. Whether it's enhancing your own attributes or attracting more powerful enemies, the choice is up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/d00d4ff6e41c315aeb0cfd0f4e064064.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/d6218ead3138aa9838183491aefad272.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/d6218ead3138aa9838183491aefad272.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/d6218ead3138aa9838183491aefad272.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Make thorough preparations, and don't get overwhelmed by the tide of enemies! The duration of battles will gradually increase, and you will face more and more fearsome elite enemies. Every combat offers a new challenge! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After this early access release, we hope you'll head to our game community or official channels to share your feedback, helping us improve the game for an even better experience down the line.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/8b14f29a552aa43ac71743f08ebc3514.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/1eff50f4913f5b80a3f3c8b485cdce52.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/1eff50f4913f5b80a3f3c8b485cdce52.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/1eff50f4913f5b80a3f3c8b485cdce52.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In multiplayer mode, you will compete against another player. Use new relics and skills to see who can fight to the end under dual pressure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/0aa402b6dba2dcbfc3f237ea60b19646.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/8b70e069a268097d109303a44f1f0f33.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/8b70e069a268097d109303a44f1f0f33.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/8b70e069a268097d109303a44f1f0f33.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Bears, bees, cacti... Various summons wil