video/mp4\"></video></span>Multiple choices of characters, smash your enemies with different tactics! Unconventional approach or  overwhelming firepower? Melee lover or ranged mastery? Only the most suitable choices ensure survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/419ecb4ef85d065727657ce33717606d.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/89f3756a5f3d5b7591d4bdb660b12da8.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/89f3756a5f3d5b7591d4bdb660b12da8.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/89f3756a5f3d5b7591d4bdb660b12da8.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>After each combat, unexpected relics will enrich your journey. Whether it's enhancing your own attributes or attracting more powerful enemies, the choice is up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/d00d4ff6e41c315aeb0cfd0f4e064064.avif?t=1768795603\" width=720 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/d6218ead3138aa9838183491aefad272.poster.avif?t=1768795603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/d6218ead3138aa9838183491aefad272.webm?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884590/extras/d6218ead3138aa9838183491aefad272.mp4?t=1768795603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Make thorough preparations, and don't get overwhelmed by the tide of enemies! The duration of battles will gradually increase, and you will face more and more fearsome elite enemies. Every combat offers a new challenge! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After this early access release, we hope you'll head to our game community or official channels to share your feedback, helping us improve the game for an even better experience down the line.</p>",
